stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> claimed: DEV worker lock
  claimed --> materializing_spec
  materializing_spec --> ready_for_stage: spec created/attached
  materializing_spec --> blocked: invalid target or missing context
  ready_for_stage --> stage_active: worktree/chat created
  stage_active --> dev_done: Reviewer complete
  stage_active --> blocked: run failed or guard blocked
  stage_active --> cancelled
  dev_done --> waiting_user_validation
  waiting_user_validation --> approved_by_user: user approves
  waiting_user_validation --> stage_active: user requests changes
  approved_by_user --> ready_for_dev_main
  ready_for_dev_main --> integrating: merge queue claims item
  integrating --> merged_to_dev_main: validation passed
  integrating --> blocked: conflict or validation failure
  merged_to_dev_main --> ready_for_prod_promotion
  ready_for_prod_promotion --> promoting
  promoting --> promoted_to_prod
  promoting --> blocked
  blocked --> claimed: retry
  cancelled --> [*]
  failed --> [*]
  promoted_to_prod --> [*]
